high_descs: Turn left, turn left, move to end of island, turn right to face island.
Pick up knife from island.
Turn left, walk around end of island, face the apple.
Cut apple on island in thirds.
Pick up knife from island, proceed around island in a zigzag fashion, walk to counter beside microwave.
Put knife on counter to right of microwave.
Turn right, turn right, walk around island to face apple.
Pick up one third of the apple on island.
Turn right, walk toward refrigerator, turn left, walk to sink.
Fill sink, drain sink, take apple out of sink.
Turn left, walk to counter, turn right to face counter.
Place apple piece behind knife on the counter.
anns.task_desc: Put rinsed apple behind knife on counter.

high_descs: Turn right and walk towards the counter
Grab a knife from the counter
Walk to the other side of the counter
Slice the apple on the counter
Walk to the counter next to the sink
Place the knife on the counter
Walk towards the island counter
Grab a slice of the apple
Walk towards the sink
Put the slice of the apple in the sink, open the water faucet and close it
Take the slice of apple and walk next the microwave
Put the slice of apple on the counter
anns.task_desc: Slice the apple, put it in the sink, open the water faucet put the slice of apple on the counter

high_descs: Move to stand at the end of the island closest to the window.
Pick up the sharp knife with yellow handle from the island.
Move around the curve of the island to the side with stools while carrying the knife.
Use the knife to slice the apple on the island.
Carry the knife over to the dishwasher.
Place the knife on the counter above the dishwasher.
Move back around the island to the side with the stools again.
Pick up a slice of apple from the island.
Carry the apple slice to the kitchen sink.
Place the apple in the sink, turn on the water, and then remove once it's washed.
Carry the apple slice to stand in front of the dishwasher.
Place the apple slice on the counter behind the knife you previously left there.
anns.task_desc: Move a washed apple slice to the counter by a knife.
